#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s1
msgid ""
"Actions address material workforce impacts such as labor conditions,\n"
"                                diversity,\n"
"                                inclusion, health &amp; safety, training, "
"and social dialogue.\n"
"                                Resources are\n"
"                                allocated to mitigate risks, enhance "
"positive impacts, and implement\n"
"                                workforce-related programs. Actions are "
"prioritized based on\n"
"                                severity and likelihood\n"
"                                of impacts, following a mitigation "
"hierarchy: prevent, reduce,\n"
"                                remediate, promote\n"
"                                positive opportunities. Engagement with "
"workers and representatives\n"
"                                informs the\n"
"                                planning and execution of actions."
msgstr ""
"Acties richten zich op materiële effecten zoals arbeidsomstandigheden, "
"diversiteit, inclusie, gezondheid &amp; veiligheid, opleiding en sociale "
"dialoog. Middelen worden toegewezen om risico's te mitigeren, positieve "
"effecten te versterken en programma's te implementeren. Acties worden "
"geprioriteerd op basis van ernst en waarschijnlijkheid, volgens de "
"mitigatiehiërarchie: voorkomen, verminderen, herstellen en positieve kansen "
"bevorderen. Dialoog met werknemers en vertegenwoordigers informeert de "
"planning en uitvoering."

