msgid ""
"Actions and Resources in Relation to Climate Change Policies (E1-3) <span "
"class=\"d-print-none\">[Non Material]</span>"
msgstr ""
"Acties en middelen met betrekking tot klimaatveranderingsbeleid (E1-3) <span "
"class=\"d-print-none\">[Niet materieel]</span>"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_iro_management
msgid ""
"Actions and resources in relation to material sustainability matters [MDR-A]"
msgstr ""
"Acties en middelen met betrekking tot materiële duurzaamheidsaangelegenheden "
"[MDR-A]"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e2
msgid ""
"Actions are backed by dedicated resources, cross-functional teams,\n"
"                                and capital\n"
"                                investment. Link actions clearly to the "
"corresponding pollution\n"
"                                policies (E2-1)."
msgstr ""
"Acties worden ondersteund door toegewezen middelen, multifunctionele teams "
"en kapitaalinvesteringen. Koppel acties duidelijk aan het overeenkomstige "
"vervuilingsbeleid (E2-1)."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e3
msgid ""
"Actions focus on <strong>avoiding</strong>, <strong>reducing</strong>,\n"
"                                and <strong>\n"
"                                    restoring</strong> water and marine "
"impacts. Resources are\n"
"                                allocated through environmental budgets, "
"with performance monitored\n"
"                                via specific water-related KPIs."
msgstr ""
"Acties zijn gericht op het <strong>vermijden, verminderen en herstellen</"
"strong> van effecten op water en het mariene milieu. Middelen worden "
"toegewezen via milieubudgetten, waarbij de prestaties worden gemonitord via "
"specifieke watergerelateerde KPI's."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e4
msgid ""
"Actions follow the mitigation hierarchy: avoidance, reduction,\n"
"                                restoration, and\n"
"                                offsetting. Local communities and indigenous "
"knowledge are\n"
"                                incorporated.\n"
"                                Biodiversity offsets are documented with "
"area, type, quality\n"
"                                criteria, and\n"
"                                standards."
msgstr ""
"Acties volgen de mitigatiehiërarchie: vermijding, vermindering, herstel en "
"compensatie. Lokale gemeenschappen en inheemse kennis worden geïntegreerd. "
"Biodiversiteitscompensaties worden gedocumenteerd met oppervlakte, type, "
"kwaliteitscriteria en standaarden."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_b7
msgid ""
"Actions implemented by {{ company_name }} to support its circular economy "
"approach and improve waste management:"
msgstr ""
"Maatregelen die door {{ company_name }} zijn geïmplementeerd ter "
"ondersteuning van de circulaire economie-aanpak en ter verbetering van het "
"afvalbeheer:"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s4
msgid ""
"Actions include\n"
"                                            product redesigns,\n"
"                                            privacy-compliance programs, "
"recall campaigns, and\n"
"                                            consumer education\n"
"                                            initiatives. Effectiveness is "
"measured by reductions in\n"
"                                            complaints,\n"
"                                            improved satisfaction, and "
"compliance with safety\n"
"                                            regulations."
msgstr ""
"Acties omvatten herontwerpen van producten, programma's voor privacy-"
"naleving, terugroepcampagnes en initiatieven voor consumentenvoorlichting. "
"De effectiviteit wordt gemeten door de afname van klachten, verbeterde "
"tevredenheid en naleving van veiligheidsvoorschriften."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s2
