msgid ""
"Actions target circular design, reuse, recycling, and\n"
"                                collaboration with\n"
"                                suppliers and customers. Circular business "
"models (repair,\n"
"                                product-as-a-service,\n"
"                                take-back) are being developed to close "
"material loops."
msgstr ""
"Acties zijn gericht op circulair ontwerp, hergebruik, recyclage en "
"samenwerking met leveranciers en klanten. Circulaire bedrijfsmodellen "
"(reparatie, product-as-a-service, terugname) worden ontwikkeld om "
"materiaalkringlopen te sluiten."

