msgid ""
"All confirmed incidents are tracked, documented, and remediated with\n"
"                                disciplinary, legal, or corrective actions. "
"Reporting includes\n"
"                                trends, root\n"
"                                causes, and measures to prevent recurrence."
msgstr ""
"Alle bevestigde incidenten worden bijgehouden, gedocumenteerd en hersteld "
"met disciplinaire, juridische of corrigerende maatregelen. Rapportage omvat "
"trends, basisoorzaken en maatregelen om herhaling te voorkomen."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_governance_c
msgid "All corporate governance bodies and committees."
msgstr "Alle organen en commissies voor ondernemingsbestuur."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s1
msgid ""
"All employees are covered by statutory or company-sponsored social\n"
"                                protection\n"
"                                schemes, including health insurance, "
"parental leave, and pension\n"
"                                benefits. Coverage\n"
"                                extends to non-employee workers where "
"legally required or\n"
"                                voluntarily adopted."
msgstr ""
"Alle werknemers vallen onder wettelijke of door de onderneming gesponsorde "
"regelingen voor sociale bescherming, waaronder ziektekostenverzekering, "
"ouderschapsverlof en pensioenregelingen. De dekking strekt zich uit tot niet-"
"werknemers waar dit wettelijk vereist is of vrijwillig is ingevoerd."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s2
msgid ""
"All reports are tracked and followed\n"
"                                    up through the supplier-management "
"system."
msgstr "Alle meldingen worden opgevolgd via het leveranciersbeheersysteem."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_basic_for_prepation
msgid ""
"All sustainability disclosures align with the same reporting period as the\n"
"                        financial year ending <strong>{{ date_end }}</"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Alle duurzaamheidstoelichtingen hebben betrekking op dezelfde "
"rapportageperiode als het\n"
"                        boekjaar dat eindigt op <strong>{{ date_end }}</"
"strong> ."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_b8
msgid ""
"All workforce-related data presented in this section are collected through "
"the Employee App, which tracks information on gender, contract type, salary, "
"location, department, and other relevant employment metrics."
msgstr ""
"Alle personeelsgerelateerde gegevens die in deze sectie worden "
"gepresenteerd, worden verzameld via de Werknemers-app, die informatie "
"bijhoudt over geslacht, contracttype, salaris, locatie, afdeling en andere "
"relevante werkgerelateerde indicatoren."

