#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid "Data Collection Methods"
msgstr "Methoden voor gegevensverzameling"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid "Data Sources"
msgstr "Gegevensbronnen"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are collected through Continuous Emissions Monitoring Systems (CEMS) "
"for air\n"
"                pollutants (e.g., NOₓ, SOₓ, PM), complemented by periodic "
"sampling and laboratory\n"
"                analyses for water and soil parameters."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden verzameld via Continuous Emissions Monitoring Systems (CEMS) "
"voor luchtverontreinigende stoffen (bijv. NOₓ, SOₓ, fijnstof), aangevuld met "
"periodieke bemonstering en laboratoriumanalyses voor water- en "
"bodemparameters."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Data are collected through Human Resources Information Systems (HRIS), "
"payroll,\n"
"                attendance, learning management, and occupational safety "
"systems. Additional\n"
"                information comes from employee surveys, grievance "
"platforms, and union or works\n"
"                council reports."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden verzameld via personeelsinformatiesystemen (HRIS), "
"loonadministratie, tijdsregistratie, leermanagementsystemen en systemen voor "
"arbeidsveiligheid. Aanvullende informatie is afkomstig uit "
"werknemersenquêtes, klachtenplatformen en rapporten van vakbonden of "
"ondernemingsraden."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Data are collected through field surveys, participatory consultations,\n"
"                        project monitoring systems, and third-party reports. "
"Where direct data are\n"
"                        unavailable, estimates or external databases are "
"used."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden verzameld via veldonderzoeken, participatieve raadplegingen, "
"projectmonitoringsystemen en rapporten van derden. Wanneer directe gegevens "
"niet beschikbaar zijn, worden schattingen of externe databases gebruikt."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are collected through material flow analysis (MFA), life-cycle\n"
"                    assessment (LCA), and internal production monitoring "
"systems. Information covers\n"
"                    inputs (raw, renewable, and secondary materials) and "
"outputs (products,\n"
"                    packaging, and waste). When primary data are "
"unavailable, supplier declarations\n"
"                    and modeled estimates are used following EU "
"Environmental Footprint or ISO 14044\n"
"                    standards."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden verzameld via materiaalstroomanalyse (MFA), "
"levenscyclusanalyse (LCA) en interne productiemonitoringsystemen. De "
"informatie bestrijkt input (ruwe, hernieuwbare en secundaire materialen) en "
"output (producten, verpakkingen en afval). Wanneer primaire gegevens niet "
"beschikbaar zijn, worden verklaringen van leveranciers en gemodelleerde "
"schattingen gebruikt volgens de EU Environmental Footprint-normen of ISO "
"14044-normen."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_governance_c
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid "Data are collected through:"
msgstr "Gegevens worden verzameld via:"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e3
msgid ""
"Data are compiled from\n"
"                                    site-level monitoring, covering both "
"direct measurements and\n"
"                                    modeled estimates. Reporting follows "
"the<em>\n"
"                                        <strong> GHG Protocol Water Guidance "
"and the WRI Aqueduct\n"
"                                    risk tool</strong>\n"
"                                    </em>."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden samengesteld op basis van monitoring op locatieniveau, "
"waarbij zowel directe metingen als gemodelleerde schattingen worden "
"gebruikt. Rapportage volgt <em>de <strong>GHG Protocol Water Guidance en de "
"WRI Aqueduct risk tool</strong></em>."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_governance_c
msgid ""
"Data are consolidated and reviewed internally by compliance, internal audit, "
"and\n"
"                sustainability teams."
msgstr ""
"egevens worden geconsolideerd en intern beoordeeld door de teams voor "
"conformiteit, interne audit en duurzaamheid."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Data are consolidated and reviewed internally by consumer experience, "
"product\n"
"                        safety, compliance, or sustainability teams."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden intern geconsolideerd door teams voor consumentenervaring, "
"productveiligheid, naleving of duurzaamheid."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Data are consolidated and reviewed internally by the HR and sustainability "
"teams."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden intern geconsolideerd en beoordeeld door de HR- en "
"duurzaamheidsteams."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are gathered from site-level environmental surveys, GIS and\n"
"                    remote-sensing tools, and ecological monitoring "
"programs. Key indicators include\n"
"                    land use, habitat condition, and species presence, "
"measured against recognized\n"
"                    frameworks such as IUCN Habitat Classification or TNFD "
"guidelines. When direct\n"
"                    data are unavailable, modeled estimates or external "
"databases (e.g., GBIF, IPBES\n"
"                    regional data) are used."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden verzameld via milieuonderzoeken per locatie, GIS- en remote-"
"sensing-tools en ecologische monitoringprogramma's. Belangrijke indicatoren "
"zijn onder meer landgebruik, conditie van de habitat en de aanwezigheid van "
"soorten, gemeten tegen erkende kaders zoals de IUCN Habitat Classification "
"of TNFD-richtlijnen. Wanneer directe gegevens niet beschikbaar zijn, worden "
"gemodelleerde schattingen of externe databases (bv. GBIF, regionale IPBES-"
"gegevens) gebruikt."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are obtained through direct flow measurements, smart meters, or\n"
"                supplier-provided utility records. In areas where direct "
"monitoring is not\n"
"                available, estimates are based on production volumes, water "
"intensity factors, or\n"
"                modeled consumption data."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden verkregen via directe debietmetingen, slimme meters of door "
"leveranciers verstrekte verbruiksoverzichten. In gebieden waar directe "
"monitoring niet beschikbaar is, zijn schattingen gebaseerd op "
"productievolumes, waterintensiteitsfactoren of gemodelleerde "
"verbruiksgegevens."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are reviewed by the environmental management team and verified by "
"accredited\n"
"                third parties under ISO 14001 or equivalent standards."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden beoordeeld door het milieumanagementteam en geverifieerd "
"door geaccrediteerde derden onder ISO 14001 of gelijkwaardige normen."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are reviewed internally by sustainability and environmental experts.\n"
"                    Where relevant, external assurance is performed under "
"recognized standards\n"
"                    (e.g., ISO 14001 Environmental Management Systems, IUCN "
"methodologies)."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden intern beoordeeld door experts op het gebied van "
"duurzaamheid en milieu. Waar relevant wordt externe assurance uitgevoerd "
"onder erkende normen (bv. ISO 14001 milieumanagementsystemen, IUCN-"
"methodologieën)."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Data are reviewed internally by sustainability, social-impact, or CSR\n"
"                        specialists. Third-party assurance is performed for "
"high-risk projects or\n"
"                        regions, following recognized standards (e.g., "
"AA1000 Assurance Standard,\n"
"                        ISO 26000 guidelines)."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden intern beoordeeld door specialisten op het gebied van "
"duurzaamheid, sociale impact of MVO. Externe assurance wordt uitgevoerd voor "
"hoog-risico-projecten of -regio's, volgens erkende normen (bv. AA1000 "
"Assurance Standard, ISO 26000-richtlijnen)."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_environmental_a
msgid ""
"Data are verified internally by the environmental management team and, "
"where\n"
"                applicable, externally assured under ISO 14046 (Water "
"Footprint) or ISO 14001."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens worden intern geverifieerd door het milieumanagementteam en, waar "
"van toepassing, extern gecontroleerd onder ISO 14046 (watervoetafdruk) of "
"ISO 14001."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c5
msgid "Data can come from HR, payroll, or contractor management systems."
