"van {{ total_reporting }} werknemers."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c1
msgid ""
"Financial materiality combines magnitude and likelihood (1-5) into a "
