#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e1
msgid ""
"The assessment also considers potential climate-related\n"
"                                opportunities,\n"
"                                including\n"
"                                renewable-energy development, low-carbon "
"products, and process\n"
"                                efficiency\n"
"                                gains."
msgstr ""
"De beoordeling houdt ook rekening met potentiële klimaatgerelateerde kansen, "
"zoals de ontwikkeling van hernieuwbare energie, koolstofarme producten en "
"efficiëntieverbeteringen in processen."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e2
msgid ""
"The assessment also identifies potential opportunities, such as\n"
"                                process efficiency\n"
"                                gains, cleaner production technologies, and "
"eco-innovation that\n"
"                                reduce environmental\n"
"                                impacts and operational costs."
msgstr ""
"De beoordeling identificeert ook kansen, zoals procesefficiëntie, schonere "
"productietechnologieën en eco-innovatie die de milieu-impact en operationele "
"kosten verminderen."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c1
msgid ""
"The assessment is governed by the ESG/DMA team, in coordination with the "
"enterprise risk management function.\n"
"                                Results are validated by executive "
"leadership and relevant board committees, ensuring alignment with strategic "
"priorities.\n"
"                                Material issues identified feed directly "
"into strategic planning, investment decisions, and operational improvements."
msgstr ""
"De beoordeling wordt uitgevoerd door het ESG-/DMA-team, in samenwerking met "
"de afdeling Enterprise Risk Management.\n"
"                                De resultaten worden gevalideerd door het "
"uitvoerend management en relevante bestuurscommissies, om afstemming met de "
"strategische prioriteiten te waarborgen.\n"
"                                Identificeerde materiële kwesties worden "
"direct meegenomen in de strategische planning, investeringsbeslissingen en "
"operationele verbeteringen."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c1
msgid ""
"The assessment is updated <strong>[specify review frequency]</strong>, or "
"sooner if significant operational or regulatory changes occur.\n"
"                                Continuous stakeholder feedback supports "
"refinement of the methodology, including updates to scoring, thresholds, and "
"evaluation criteria as the risk landscape evolves."
msgstr ""
"De beoordeling wordt <strong>[specificeer beoordelingsfrequentie]</strong> "
"bijgewerkt, of eerder indien er belangrijke operationele of regelgevende "
"wijzigingen plaatsvinden.\n"
"                                Voortdurende feedback van belanghebbenden "
"ondersteunt de verfijning van de methodologie, inclusief updates van scores, "
"drempelwaarden en evaluatiecriteria naarmate het risicolandschap evolueert."

