#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c2
msgid "Workers in the Value Chain"
msgstr "Werknemers in de waardeketen"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:ir.actions.act_window,help:esg_csrd.action_view_metrics
msgid "Workers in the value chain"
msgstr "Werknemers in de waardeketen"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid "Workforce Data Collection Methods"
msgstr "Methoden voor het verzamelen van personeelsgegevens"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s1
msgid ""
"Workforce characteristics are collected for employees workers,\n"
"                                covering demographics,\n"
"                                employment type, contract, and geographical "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"Kenmerken van het personeelsbestand worden verzameld voor werknemers, met "
"betrekking tot demografie, type dienstverband, contract en geografische "
"spreiding."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s1
msgid ""
"Workforce characteristics are collected for non-employee workers,\n"
"                                covering\n"
"                                demographics, employment type, contract, and "
"geographical\n"
"                                distribution."
msgstr ""
"Kenmerken van het personeelsbestand worden verzameld voor niet-werknemers, "
"met betrekking tot demografie, type tewerkstelling, contract en geografische "
"spreiding."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Workforce data are collected from supplier HR records, worker surveys,\n"
"                third-party audits, grievance and whistleblowing reports, "
"and training and\n"
"                capacity-building records."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens over het personeelsbestand worden verzameld uit HR-archieven van "
"leveranciers, werknemersenquêtes, audits door derden, klachten- en "
"klokkenluidersrapporten en verslagen van trainingen en capaciteitsopbouw."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Workforce data are reviewed internally by sustainability and HR "
"specialists.\n"
"                For high-risk suppliers or regions, third-party assurance is "
"performed under\n"
"                recognized standards, such as SA8000 or ISO 45001."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens over het personeelsbestand worden intern beoordeeld door "
"duurzaamheids- en HR-specialisten. Voor hoog-risico-leveranciers of -regio's "
"wordt externe assurance uitgevoerd onder erkende normen, zoals SA8000 of ISO "
"45001."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_appendix_social_b
msgid ""
"Workforce data include all employees and non-employee workers under "
"<strong>{{ company_name }}</strong>'s direct management or operational "
"control."
msgstr ""
"Gegevens over het personeelsbestand omvatten alle werknemers en niet-"
"werknemers die onder het directe beheer of de operationele controle van "
"<strong>{{ company_name }}</strong> vallen."

#. module: esg_csrd
